[dependencies]
actix-rt = "1.1.1"
actix-web = "2.0.0" src/main.rs use actix_web::{get, App, HttpServer, Responder}; #[get("/")]
async fn index() -> impl Responder { format!("Hello World!")
} #[actix_rt::main]
async fn main() -> std::io::Result<()> { HttpServer::new(|| { App::new() .service(index)) }) .bind("127.0.0.1:3000")? .run() .await
}
